courseDescription:
This course, Management Skills for Business Professionals, will provide you with an understanding of the various knowledge management, meeting management, and crisis management skills you will find useful when managing a professional business. You will learn the knowledge management life cycle. You will be able to explain the new knowledge management paradigm. You will also learn about implementing knowledge management in your organization.

This course then explains managing meetings. You will learn about some of the important parts about planing a meeting like choosing a time and place, gathering materials, and setting up the meeting. You will also learn about chairing a meeting, dealing with disruptions, and taking minutes.

This course then wraps up with crisis management where you will learn about escalation of workplace violence, triggers of violence, concerning behaviors and indicators. You will learn response to workplace violence and strategies to escalate and prevent violence before it starts. By taking this course you will learn important skills for management in a professional business. So why wait? Start learning today.

Start Course Now

Once you have completed this diploma course, you have the option to acquire an official Diploma, which is a great way to share your achievement with the world.

Your Alison diploma is:
  • Ideal for sharing with potential employers
  • Include it in your CV, professional social media profiles and job applications.
  • An indication of your commitment to continuously learn, upskill & achieve high results.
  • An incentive for you to continue empowering yourself through lifelong learning.
Alison offers 3 types of Diplomas for completed Diploma courses:
  • Digital diploma: a downloadable diploma in PDF format immediately available to you when you complete your purchase.
  • diploma: a physical version of your officially branded and security-marked diploma, posted to you with FREE shipping.
  • Framed diploma: a physical version of your officially branded and security marked diploma in a stylish frame, posted to you with FREE shipping.

modules.name: Module
modules.description: In this module, Knowledge Management, students will gain an understanding of knowledge management. Students will learn about the dos and don'ts of knowledge management. The module will cover the knowledge management life cycle and the new knowledge management rationale. It will also go over customizing knowledge management in your organization and give students tips for success
topics: Implementing Knowledge Management in Your Organization

modules.name: Module
modules.description: In this module, Meeting Management, students will learn about various skills for setting up a verity of meetings in a verity of settings. Students This module will teach students about choosing the time and place for a meeting. Students will learn about electronic options for meetings. The course will also cover meeting roles like chairing the meeting. You will also learn about taking minutes and making the most of your meeting.
topics: Making the Most of Your Meeting

modules.name: Module
modules.description: In this module, Crisis Management, students will learn about crisis management in the workplace. Students will learn about workplace violence. The module will also go over concerning behaviors and escalation. The module will cover triggers of workplace violence and conflict dangers. Students will also learn about some of the indicators of domestic violence. The module will also cover strategies and response.
